			</div>

			<div class="services-list">
				<h3>Our Elgin HVAC Services Include:</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Air conditioning installation, repair, and maintenance</li>
					<li>Heating system installation and repair</li>
					<li>Emergency HVAC service</li>
